The most common interiew question in NYC

What are you looking for?


... What's the ideal answer to this question?

I usually say a it's a combination of things:
i) I'm looking for a good fit for my skillset
ii) I love being data scientist because it gives me the chance exercise my diversity of skills from business acumen, engineering and analysis.
iii) A position where I could contribute the most given my skills I just mentioned. 